<head>
    <title>About Us</title>
    <style>
        /* Header styling */
        h1 {
            display: inline-block; /* Makes the underline span only the text */
            border-bottom: 2px solid lightgrey; /* Thin line under the headers */
            padding-bottom: 5px; /* Optional: Adds space between text and the underline */
            margin-bottom: 20px; /* Adjust the spacing between the header and the text below */
            color: #6B9080; /* Header text color */
            text-align: center; /* Center align the header */
            font-weight: bold; /* Make the header bold */

        }

        /* Light grey background for the "About Us" section only */
        .about-us-section {
            background-color: #A4C3B2; /* Light grey background for the section */
            padding: 70px 40px; /* Padding around the content */
            margin: 20px auto; /* Centers the section */
            max-width: 1300px; /* Limit the width */
            text-align: center; /* Center align the header */

        }

        .about-us-section h1 {
            color: white; 
        }

        .about-us-section .text-content {
            color: white; 
            font-size: 20px; /* Increase the font size for readability */

        }

        /* Body padding for better spacing */
        body {
            padding: 20px;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif; /* Clean font */
            margin: 0; /* Remove default body margin */
            background-color: #f4f4f4; /* Optional: Lighter background for the body */
        }

        /* Text content styling */
        .text-content {
            font-size: 1.1em; /* Slightly larger text for readability */
            line-height: 1.6; /* Increase line spacing for better readability */
            margin-bottom: 20px; /* Space between paragraphs */

        }

        /* Section for the other content without background */
        .normal-section {
            padding: 40px 20px;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 10px auto;

        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- About Us Section with light grey background -->
  <div class="about-us-section">
    <h1>About Us</h1>
    <p class="text-content">
        At Colorado Community Resource Finder, we are committed to empowering Colorado's low-income residents, 
        people experiencing homelessness, immigrants and migrants by providing a centralized, user-friendly platform 
        to discover free or low-cost resources in essential areas such as food, housing, healthcare, childcare, legal services, and education.
    </p>

    <p class="text-content">
        Our vision is to build a stronger, more connected community by ensuring that everyone in Colorado has access to the 
        resources they need to thrive. By centralizing knowledge and creating a space for feedback and collaboration, 
        we aim to make navigating these services easier and more transparent for all.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Other Sections without light grey background -->
  <div class="normal-section">
    <h1>Who We Are</h1>
    <p class="text-content">
        We are a team focused on providing an easy-to-use platform where users can find, post, and rate free or low-cost resources.
        Our web app organizes resources into categories such as food, housing, healthcare, legal services, education, and childcare.
        By centralizing this information, we aim to make it easier for individuals to access the services they need, with a simple
        interface for both users and contributors.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="normal-section">
    <h1>How can I use COmmunity?</h1>
    <p class="text-content">COmmunity aims to be an easy-to-use interface where users can view, save, and access resources in a centralized
        location. We have partnered with various organizations in order to provide these services through a free computer application. 
    </p>
    <p class="text-content">
        <b>Logged in users</b> will be able to:
        <br> ✔ save and rate events
        <br> ✔ submit reviews 
        <br> ✔ suggest free / low cost events or resources for the public
        <br> ✔ get personalized suggestions for events and outreach programs
    </p>
